column5:
Introducing the Google Pixel 4a 5G – Your gateway to the future of mobile technology. This sleek and sophisticated smartphone combines the best of Google's innovation in a budget-friendly package.
**Stunning Display:** The Pixel 4a 5G features a vibrant 6.2-inch OLED display, providing sharp and vivid visuals for all your content. Whether you're streaming movies or scrolling through your social media feed, you'll be captivated by the stunning picture quality.
**5G Connectivity:** Experience the next level of connectivity with 5G support. Stream, download, and game faster than ever before, all while enjoying seamless video calls and lightning-fast data speeds.
**Impressive Camera:** Capture memories in exceptional detail with the Pixel 4a 5G's remarkable camera system. The 12.2MP main camera and 16MP ultra-wide lens ensure stunning photos in various lighting conditions. Google's renowned Night Sight technology allows you to take incredible low-light shots.
**All-Day Battery:** Stay powered up throughout the day with the Pixel 4a 5G's long-lasting battery. Whether you're working, playing, or streaming, this smartphone will keep up with your demands.
**Pure Android Experience:** Enjoy the latest Android updates and features as soon as they're released, thanks to Google's pure Android experience. Say goodbye to bloatware and enjoy a clean, user-friendly interface.
**Google Assistant:** With the Pixel 4a 5G, you have a personal Google Assistant at your fingertips. Just say "Hey Google" to get answers, manage your tasks, and control smart devices effortlessly.
**Security:** Rest easy knowing your data is secure with the Titan M security chip and frequent security updates.
The Google Pixel 4a 5G is the ideal choice for those who crave exceptional performance, photography, and connectivity without breaking the bank. It's the smartphone designed to keep you connected to what matters most in your life. Elevate your mobile experience with the Pixel 4a 5G today!
(Important note: This device has a high processor and high resolution display so heating up is common. No refund will issue if the mobile seal (sticker) is removed)

column5:
Smartphone brand Sparx has launched S3 smartphones in local markets recently.
This is a budget smartphone that offers a package of all the latest features that you could possibly want.
Sparx has made the S3 affordable for everyone by utilizing the latest hardware and software technologies.
This has allowed them to make a quality handset at a budget-friendly price, allowing customers to get the most out of their money.
First and foremost, the massive 5.45 Inches IPS LCD Capacitive Touchscreen display of the Sparx's S3 gives it a very premium look from an aesthetic perspective.
In fact, it's an HD display that is capable of displaying 720x1600 pixels very clearly.
After that, this brand new Sparx S3's Dual Cameras with 5 MP and 0.3 MP as well as a brighter LED flash for better light quality.
It will be equipped with a single 2MP selfie camera on the front that will be able to take beautiful portraits.
Aside from that, this S3 is powered by the well-known Unisoc SC9832E chipset with the addition of a 1.4Ghz Quad Core CPU for smooth and error-free operation without any lags or lag errors.
A big 2700mAh battery is featured on this S3 phone which ensures that it will easily last the whole day when recharged once. Also, there are no confirmed details about the Sparx S3 that will be released in the near future.
We will be updating you as soon as we have more information.

The Oppo A57 is a mid-range Android smartphone. It was part of Oppo's lineup of mobile devices and offered a set of features suitable for everyday use. Here's some additional information about the Oppo A57:
Design and Display:
The Oppo A57 features a 5.2-inch IPS LCD capacitive touchscreen with a resolution of 720 x 1280 pixels. It has a metal unibody design, which gives it a premium feel.
Performance:
The phone is powered by the Qualcomm Snapdragon 435 chipset, which includes an octa-core CPU clocked at 1.4 GHz and an Adreno 505 GPU. This configuration allows for smooth operation of everyday tasks and moderate gaming.
Storage:
It comes with 32GB of internal storage for apps, media, and files, along with 3GB of RAM for multitasking. It also has a dedicated microSD card slot that supports cards up to 256GB for expandable storage.
Camera:
The Oppo A57 features a 13-megapixel rear camera with phase detection autofocus and an LED flash, making it capable of taking decent photos. Its standout feature is the 16-megapixel front camera, designed for better-quality selfies.
Battery:
The device is equipped with a 2900 mAh non-removable battery. The battery capacity may offer moderate usage on a single charge.
Operating System:
It runs on Android 6.0 (Marshmallow) with Oppo's custom ColorOS 3.0 user interface.
Connectivity:
The Oppo A57 supports dual SIM cards and 4G LTE connectivity. It includes standard features like Wi-Fi, Bluetooth 4.1, and a micro USB 2.0 port.
Other Features:
Notable features of the Oppo A57 include a 3.5mm audio jack for headphones, and it supports USB On-The-Go (OTG) for connecting USB accessories.

DETAILS OF INFINIX SMART 7 4GB RAM 64GB ROM.Infinix is near to launch Smart 7 series of smartphones and it has been suggested that the devices may be launched in the upcoming months of this year, based on recent leaks.Then let's move on to the latest features of the Infinix Smart 7.Topping the list of features is a dual-lens camera setup, a 6.6-inch full-HD+ display, and a massive 6000 mAh battery with fast charging.In light of the fact that the smartphone might be launched with a massive 6000mAh battery pack, it is likely that users of this phone will be able to use it all day long on a single charge.Furthermore this Infinix Smart 7's a powerful Helio A22 SoC chipset with a couple of Octa-core CPUs.A dedicated memory card slot will enable users to expand the cell phone's memory up to 256GB in addition to the smartphone's 64GB of internal storage.
There is no doubt that the Infinix Smart 7 is very attractive due to its dual camera setup along with its attractive design.The phone's primary camera sensor is 13 MP, while the second is a 0.3 MP macro sensor.There is a single 5MP camera with an LED flashlight located on the front of the device.The brand new Infinix Smart's 7 is packed with a bigger 6.6 Inches TFT LCD display that can easily support the HD resolution of 720 x 1612 Pixels beside them it offers 500 nits of extra brightness.The improved display of the Infinix Smart's 7 allows for richer and more vibrant colours, greater clarity and better visibility in direct sunlight, making it an ideal device for watching movies, playing games, and browsing the web.The improved brightness also ensures that users will be able to use the device more comfortably in direct sunlight and other bright environments.

Capture more moments with Triple Camera
Turn your gallery into a treasure trove of photos taken with your creative touch. Snap memorable moments in clear detail with the 50MP Main Camera.

Bring the focus to the front with Depth Camera
The 2MP Depth Camera lets you adjust the depth of field in your photos. Adjust the background blur for high-quality portrait shots that make your subject truly stand out.
Portrait On 
Portrait Off

Keep going with a powerful battery
The 5,000mAh (typical)¹ battery lets you keep doing what you do, for hours on end. AI power management detects and adjusts to your mobile usage habits for long-lasting power.
Powerful Octa-core processor for fast performance
Galaxy A04s combines Octa-core processing power with up to 4GB of RAM for fast and efficient performance for the task at hand. Enjoy 64GB of internal storage and add up to 1TB more with microSD card.
Go beyond the listening experience with Dolby Atmos
Simply plug in your headphones and you’ll be transported to the middle of your music and movies. With Dolby Atmos, you'll hear sound that's full, loud and seems to surround you in the scene.
Protect what matters to you
Built into the phone's hardware and software from the start, Samsung Knox protects your phone from the minute it's turned on. Offering multi-layered security, it defends your most sensitive information from malware and malicious threats.
 Unlock your phone with your fingerprint
With the fingerprint sensor built right into the power button, one seamless motion gets you into your phone.
